Also in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">New York</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Israel Silverman</ENAMEX> , an insurance - company lawyer , comments that program trading `` increases volatility , but I do n't think it should be banned .
There 's no culprit here .
