Arbitraging on differences between spot and futures prices is an important part of many financial markets , he says .
He adds that his shares in a company savings plan are invested in a mutual fund , and volatility , on <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">a given day</ENAMEX> , may hurt the fund .
